         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#ala2004">
            <p>i.  In fear approach the gate of the <foreign xml:lang="la">bema</foreign>.</p>
            <p>ii. Jesus Christ is victorious,</p>
            <p>iii. Lord, help your servant Philippos, a sinner. Amen.</p>
